title: Static X Discography (includes Cult of Static)
description:
Ok, got a Static X Discography here that is full and complete and all that.

Includes the albums:
Beneath, Between, Beyond (this album is mostly demos and covers, still good stuff)
Cannibal (featuring the song Destroyer)
Cult of Static (featuring the song Stingwray)
Machine (featuring the song Cold)
Shadow Zone
Start A War (featuring the songs Skinnyman and Dirthouse)
and Wisconsin Death Trip (IMO their best album.  features the songs I'm With Stupid, Push It and Bled for Days)

anyway, enjoy the torrent and one of the greatest bands ever!
